long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Send ChatGPT with WhatsApp

SendGPT is a tool that allows users to send ChatGPT conversations with WhatsApp.

ChatGPT is a powerful language processing artificial intelligence.

With SendGPT you can send your chat conversations to your friends and family through WhatsApp. These conversations can take on a variety of forms, such as witty banter with a celebrity, deep discussions with a historical figure, or humorous interactions with a chatbot. 

SendGPT is designed to provide a new and exciting way for users to communicate with their friends and family, and to share their favorite conversations with others. With SendGPT, users can add some novelty and entertainment to their messaging routine.


WhatsApp is a trademark of WhatsApp LLC. 
This extension is not related in any way to WhatsApp.
